name: Painful years
description: We can say that these years were the most painful and shameful years in the history of the world. How can the cruelty and torture of one of the world's worst men be erased from memory? I wish it had never happened, I wish it had never been remembered, and I wish it had never been in our memories. No matter how many generations come after us, we should never forget these sufferings and humanity should not be trampled on again.
